      "value": "<div title=\"Page 50\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div title=\"Page 50\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>Your particular brand of fire magic can superheat air or water instead of producing fire, allowing your spells to remain effective underwater.</p>\n<div title=\"Page 51\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<p><strong>Benefit</strong>: Your spells, spell-like abilities, and supernatural abilities that deal fire damage deal an additional amount of fire damage equal to half your level (minimum 1), and they deal full damage underwater.</p>\n<p><strong>Normal</strong>: Fire damage deals one-quarter damage underwater.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
